uek_drama.param_02: Woooow!\nIt's grown so huge...\nHow crazy is that?! ☆
I am no longer able\nto see from here\nhow far it has reached.
With things like this,\ndon't you get the urge\nto see what's at the top?!
I can understand that.\nBesides, it might help us\nlearn what caused this.
Well, I'm curious too,\nso I guess I'll tag along.
Yay!\nLet's all do our best\nto climb to the top!
Hah hah hah hah!\nThis is my first step\nto world domination!
Hey, Karyl!\nYou've gotta take a\nlook at this view! ☆
Hey, stop that!\nQuit pulling!\nYou'll make me fall!
Eheh. I feel certain\nthat more grand vistas\nawait us higher up.
The Balloon Bird\ncatches the Wyvern!\nLet's get moving!

The expression is
"the early bird
catches the worm,"
you know, Rino...
I'm going to climb\nthe stairs to adulthood!
And I'm gonna be\nthe top of all models!
I'd be a lame hero\nif I couldn't brave a\nmeasly height like this!
Yes, this seems like\npretty good training.\nI'm starting to enjoy it.
I-I can't get enough\nof the way these vines\nwrap around my feet...
Wh-whoa! Are we\nstanding on clouds?\nIs that possible?!
It certainly is\na funny feeling!\nSo soft and fluffy! ♪
They seem solid enough\nto hold our weight...\nbut let's be careful.
Ahh... Everything has\ngone white... Chris,\nyou should be careful!
Hahahah. You're sinking\nfrom your armor's weight!\nLet me pull you up! ☆

These clouds are
mighty cute...
I sure would love to
take one home! ♪
That may not be\nthe most realistic\nof plans...
We have now reached\nquite a remarkable\nheight. And yet...
I still can't even\nsee the top!\nHow tall is this thing?!
Oh, don't worry!\nFood always tastes\nbetter after exercise! ☆
Urgh... Does the wind\nitself have something\nagainst loners?!
Clouds are comfys~!\nMiyako feels like\nfloating into the sky!
You too, squirt?\nI feel like my body's\ngetting lighter as well!
Try not to float\nall the way off to\nheaven, Miyako...
Miss Uzuki, we still\nhave some way to go.\nShould you not rest?
Oh, I'm still OK!\nI'm actually having\nso much fun it's crazy!
Wow, you're full of\nenergy! Uzuki, let's keep\nclimbing together! ☆
Hey, look!\nI made a great\ncloud Pukichi!
Oh, wow...!\nI'd love to try making\nsomething too... ♪
We've come a long way!\nLet's take a quick peek\ndown at the ground!
Eheh. I am glad you both\nseem to be enjoying\nyourselves so thoroughly.
Wahh! Hatsune!\nYou can't go to sleep\nin a place like that!
The breeze feels lovely.\nIts soft touch seems to\nwhisper kind words.
Maybe it's the sound\nof the violet sky above\nsummoning us closer...
I never expected\nto see the two of you\nin perfect sync...
What do you think\na rice ball-shaped cloud\nwould taste like? *drool*
Mmm, this cloud's\nso fluffy and warm...\nPerfect for napping...
Wait, I think that\ncloud's floating off!\nWh-what should we do?!
There ain't no way\nit's as soft as fresh hay!\nCome back to us, Rin!
I-I think I see him\nright over there...\n*staaaaaare*...
It's so much fun\nplaying on fluffy clouds!\nHappy times~! ♪
Yeah! You think so\ntoo, right, Kyoka?\n...BOO!
M-Misogi! It's far too\ndangerous to play\ntricks like that up here!
This will be an easy climb\nas long as we're efficient\nwith our stamina!

Ohohohoho!
What a view!
I can't wait to climb
even higher!
Even up in the clouds...\nCarmina on stage!
The wind is so pleasant!\nI can hear the spirits'\nhappy voices!
Yep, it's the best!\nLet's keep performing\nthrough to the encore!
What a lovely place!\nI should bring my students\nhere on a school trip.
Oh, really?\nPerhaps I'll bring the\nvillage children too!
Look where we are!\nWe're up in the stars!\nIsn't this amazing?! ☆
It truly is the most\nmarvelous of sights.\nLet us make the most of it.
Why are you so calm?!\nFreak out a bit more!\nThis is so not normal!
We finally found\nKuka, but now she's\nflying off again!
Are you sure she's not\nenjoying this?!
Under the light of the\nstars, my beauty shines\nbrighter than ever...

SPAAAAACE!
Space. I'm in space.
Need to see it all.
So much space.
Heheheh... The stars\nlend me their energy...\nMy awakening is nigh...!
Look—a shooting star!\nDon't forget to make\na wish, everyone.
Oh, you're right.\nThis may be the perfect\nsituation for our guild.
Okay, wish time!\nI'm gonna wish for...\nuhhh... uhhhh...!
Suzume, are you okay?!\nWe're a long way up,\nso please be careful.
Ohhh! Hey, check it out,\nShimamu, Shiburin!\nLook at all the stars!
I wonder if this is what\nthe world would look\nlike for a top idol...
We've got to shine\neven brighter than\nany of these stars!
